{"title":"Combined feed","url":"https://Vinnl.github.io/feeds/all.xml","elements":[{"title":"Pizza Cat (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that <b><a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pizza_Cat\" title=\"Pizza Cat\">Pizza Cat</a></b> <i>(pictured)</i>, a cat living at Al Udeid Air Base, was awarded the rank of \"Senior Meowster Sergeant\" by the United States Air Force?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pizza_Cat","retrieved":1783587377679},{"title":"Ælfhun (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that <b><a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ælfhun_(bishop_of_London)\" title=\"Ælfhun (bishop of London)\">Ælfhun</a></b>, Bishop of London, was accused of trying to remove the body of <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Edmund_the_Martyr\" title=\"Edmund the Martyr\">St<span typeof=\"mw:Entity\">&nbsp;</span>Edmund</a>, but the bier was said to have miraculously refused to move?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/%C3%86lfhun_(bishop_of_London)","retrieved":1783587377679},{"title":"a local official of the Joseon dynasty (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that <b><a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eom_Heung-do\" title=\"Eom Heung-do\"> a local official of the Joseon dynasty</a></b> secretly buried the body of <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Danjong_of_Joseon\" title=\"Danjong of Joseon\">King Danjong</a> despite <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sejo_of_Joseon\" title=\"Sejo of Joseon\">King Sejo</a>'s threats to kill the family of anyone who did so?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eom_Heung-do","retrieved":1783587377679},{"title":"Petal (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ariana_Grande\" title=\"Ariana Grande\">Ariana Grande</a> claimed that she would need two brains and six arms to produce her eighth album before announcing <i><b><a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Petal_(album)\" title=\"Petal (album)\">Petal</a></b></i><span style=\"padding-left:0.15em;\"><span typeof=\"mw:Entity\">?</span></span>","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Petal_(album)","retrieved":1783587377680},{"title":"a type of ballad (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that <b><a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Execution_ballad\" title=\"Execution ballad\">a type of ballad</a></b> details the fictionalized last words of executed people?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Execution_ballad","retrieved":1783587377681},{"title":"a trans woman (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that a fixture of Madrid nightlife in the 1990s was <b><a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Susie_Pop\" title=\"Susie Pop\">a trans woman</a></b> who was often seen at concerts wearing a large <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Picture_hat\" title=\"Picture hat\">picture hat</a>?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Susie_Pop","retrieved":1783587377682},{"title":"Fae Farm (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that Gambit Digital acquired the rights to the 2023 video game <i><b><a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fae_Farm\" title=\"Fae Farm\">Fae Farm</a></b></i> five days after the original developer ended online support in September<span typeof=\"mw:Entity\">&nbsp;</span>2025?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fae_Farm","retrieved":1783587377683},{"title":"Tschirnhausen cubic (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that a dog chasing its master and a crab sidestepping an intruder can both be modeled mathematically by motion along a <b><a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tschirnhausen_cubic\" title=\"Tschirnhausen cubic\">Tschirnhausen cubic</a></b>?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tschirnhausen_cubic","retrieved":1783587377685},{"title":"Hushahu (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that soon after the general <